    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克警方使用催泪瓦斯驱散抗议者和记者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/mozambique-police-use-teargas-to-disperse-protesters-in-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克警方周一发射催泪瓦斯驱散采访反对党总统候选人维南西奥·蒙德拉纳 (Venâncio Mondlane) 的记者，蒙德拉纳曾呼吁抗议周末其律师被谋杀的事件以及他所说的试图操纵 10 月 9 日选举的行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/mozambique-police-use-teargas-to-disperse-protesters-in-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:50:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南选举国家主席</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/vietnam-parliament-elects-luong-cuong-as-nation-s-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南国会已任命政治局委员梁强为国家主席，接替卸任的越南共产党中央委员会主席苏林，此举加强了政府的集体权力分享。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/vietnam-parliament-elects-luong-cuong-as-nation-s-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 09:40:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国敦促黎巴嫩和加沙冲突在选举前停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/israel-hits-hezbollah-finances-as-us-eyes-diplomacy-in-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员前往中东，做最后的努力，以确保以色列与伊朗支持的真主党和哈马斯在下月初总统大选之前停火。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/israel-hits-hezbollah-finances-as-us-eyes-diplomacy-in-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 08:45:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
